#: ../../source/applying_special_fx.rst:505
msgid ""
"As soon as an effect node is selected in the schematic, the Edit tool "
"becomes the current tool and the related effect gadgets, if available, "
"are visualized. The Edit tool settings will refer to the column the "
"effect is applied to, but in case the effect creates a computer generated"
" image (e.g. a radial gradient or a light spot) the settings will refer "
"to the effect column itself (see  :ref:`Animating Objects "
"<animating_objects>`  )."
