#: ../../source/applying_special_fx.rst:607
msgid ""
"Right-click the macro node and choose Open Macro FX from the menu that "
"opens: the macro nodes are displayed in a box, with the right links to "
"the rest of the schematic."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/applying_special_fx.rst:609
msgid ""
"When the content of a macro is displayed it is not possible to edit the "
"links between macro nodes, and links with nodes outside the macro."
